ga2O(){return"The title image shows an urban scene with multiple modes of transport: a teal bus, a cyclist on a teal bicycle, and an elevated white-and-orange train. People are walking in the background, and a large profile of a woman with dark hair is shown to the right, overlooking the city. The city has modern buildings, greenery, and statues."},
